graph TD
    A[Start: execute_instruction] --> B[Rephrase instruction]
    B --> C[Loop through rephrased actions]
    C --> D[Get nodes for current action]
    D --> E[Generate action using LLM]
    E --> F[Execute action using driver]
    F --> G{Success?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Move to next action]
    G -->|No| I{Retry limit reached?}
    I -->|No| E
    I -->|Yes| H
    H --> J{More actions?}
    J -->|Yes| C
    J -->|No| K[End: Return result]
